Title: Tina's Tasteful Tiara
Description:
It's a dazzling diamond tiara. Who in the valley would be wealthy enough to own such a piece of jewelry?

Whoever it is, they might be willing to give a nice reward.
ObjectivesText: Bring the Tasteful Tiara to Tina Mudclaw at Haohan's House or Halfhill Market in the Valley of the Four Winds.
